M|Plat|tx|\| Platform \| Best For \| Frequency \| Key Format \|
M|Plat|tx|\|----------\|----------\|-----------\|------------\|
M|Plat|tx|\| LinkedIn \| B2B, thought leadership \| 3-5x/week \| Carousels, stories \|
M|Plat|tx|\| Twitter/X \| Tech, real-time, community \| 3-10x/day \| Threads, hot takes \|
M|Plat|tx|\| Instagram \| Visual brands, lifestyle \| 1-2 posts + Stories daily \| Reels, carousels \|
