M|Cont|tx|bd your cn around 3-5 pillars that align w/ your expertise and audience interests.
M|Exam|tx|\| Pillar \| % of cn \| Topics \|
M|Exam|tx|\|--------\|--------------\|--------\|
M|Exam|tx|\| Industry in \| 30% \| tn, data, predictions \|
M|Exam|tx|\| Behind-the-scenes \| 25% \| Building the company, lessons learned \|
M|Exam|tx|\| Educational \| 25% \| How-tos, frameworks, tips \|
M|Exam|tx|\| Personal \| 15% \| Stories, values, hot takes \|
M|Exam|tx|\| Promotional \| 5% \| pd updates, offers \|
M|Pill|For |
M|Pill|tx|1. What unique perspective do you have?
M|Pill|tx|2. What questions does your audience ask?
M|Pill|tx|3. What cn has performed well before?
M|Pill|tx|4. What can you cr consistently?
M|Pill|tx|5. What aligns w/ business goals?
