M|Hook|tx|The first line determines whether anyone reads the rest.
M|Curi|it|"I was wrong abt [common belief]."
M|Curi|it|"The real reason [outcome] happens isn't what you think."
M|Curi|it|"[Impressive result] — and it only took [surprisingly short time]."
M|Stor|it|"Last week, [unexpected thing] happened."
M|Stor|it|"I almost [big mistake/fl]."
M|Stor|it|"3 years ago, I [past state]. Today, [current state]."
M|Valu|- "H|"
M|Valu|- "[|"
M|Valu|- "S|"
M|Cont|- "U|[bold statement]"
M|Cont|- "[|"
M|Cont|it|"I stopped [common practice] and [positive result]."
