M|Cont|tx|---
M|Cont|tx|Turn one piece of cn into many. The best sl cn isn't created from scratch — it's extracted from longer-form pillar cn and adapted to each platform.
M|Blog|tx|\| Platform \| Format \|
M|Blog|tx|\|----------\|--------\|
M|Blog|tx|\| LinkedIn \| Key in + link in comments \|
M|Blog|tx|\| LinkedIn \| Carousel of main points \|
M|Blog|tx|\| Twitter/X \| Thread of key takeaways \|
M|Blog|tx|\| Instagram \| Carousel w/ visuals \|
M|Blog|tx|\| Instagram \| Reel summarizing the post \|
M|Podc|Extr|
M|Podc|tx|\| Atom tp \| What to Look For \| Best Platform \|
M|Podc|tx|\|-----------\|-----------------\|---------------\|
M|Podc|tx|\| Quotable moment \| A bold claim, hot take, or memorable line (15-60 sec) \| Twitter/X, LinkedIn, TikTok \|
M|Podc|tx|\| Story arc \| A complete mini-story w/ setup, conflict, resolution (60-90 sec) \| Instagram Reels, TikTok, YouTube Shorts \|
M|Podc|tx|\| Tactical tip \| A specific how-to or framework explained clearly (30-60 sec) \| LinkedIn, YouTube Shorts \|
M|Podc|tx|\| Controversial take \| A contrarian opinion that sparks debate \| Twitter/X, LinkedIn \|
M|Podc|tx|\| Data/stat callout \| A surprising number or research finding \| LinkedIn carousel, Twitter/X \|
M|Podc|tx|\| Behind-the-scenes \| Authentic, unpolished moments \| Instagram Stories, TikTok \|
M|Podc|**Po|**
M|Podc|tx|1. **Get transcript** — use Whisper, Descript, or your podcast host's transcription
M|Podc|tx|2. **Mark timestamps** — flag the 5-10 best moments while listening or scanning transcript
M|Podc|tx|3. **Extract clips** — pull vd/audio clips for each moment (Descript, Opus Clip, or manual)
M|Podc|tx|4. **Write standalone captions** — each clip needs context; don't assume the viewer heard the rest
M|Podc|tx|5. **Add subtitles** — most sl vd is watched w/o sound
M|Podc|tx|6. **Schedule across 1-2 weeks** — spread a single episode across multiple posts
M|Podc|**Pe|**
M|Podc|it|3-5 short vd clips or audiograms (15-60 sec) for Reels/TikTok/Shorts
M|Podc|it|1-2 LinkedIn text posts from key in
M|Podc|it|1 Twitter/X thread of takeaways
M|Podc|it|1 carousel summarizing the main framework or list
M|Podc|it|1 nl section or blog post from the best segment
M|Webi|tx|\| Extract \| Format \|
M|Webi|tx|\|---------\|--------\|
M|Webi|tx|\| Key slides w/ commentary \| LinkedIn carousel \|
M|Webi|tx|\| Q&A highlights \| Twitter/X thread \|
M|Webi|tx|\| Speaker quotes \| Quote graphics for Instagram/LinkedIn \|
M|Webi|tx|\| Audience reactions/poll results \| Engagement posts \|
M|Webi|tx|\| Full recording → short clips \| Reels, TikTok, Shorts \|
M|News|tx|\| Extract \| Format \|
M|News|tx|\|---------\|--------\|
M|News|tx|\| Main in \| LinkedIn post \|
M|News|tx|\| Curated links w/ commentary \| Twitter/X thread \|
M|News|tx|\| Data or stat \| Quote graphic \|
M|News|tx|\| Hot take or opinion \| Twitter/X post, LinkedIn \|
M|Repu|tx|1. **cr pillar cn** (blog, vd, podcast, webinar, nl)
M|Repu|tx|2. **Extract cn atoms** (5-10 per piece — quotes, stories, tips, data)
M|Repu|tx|3. **Adapt to each platform** (format, length, and tone)
M|Repu|tx|4. **Write standalone captions** (each post must work w/o context)
M|Repu|tx|5. **Schedule across the week** (spread distribution, don't dump all at once)
M|Repu|tx|6. **up and reshare** (evergreen cn can repeat every 3-6 months)
M|Repu|tx|---
