M|Batc|tx|1. rv cn pillar topics
M|Batc|tx|2. Write 5 LinkedIn posts
M|Batc|tx|3. Write 3 Twitter threads + daily tweets
M|Batc|tx|4. cr Instagram carousel + Reel ideas
M|Batc|tx|5. Schedule everything
M|Batc|tx|6. Leave room for real-time engagement
M|Batc|tx|---
M|Dail|tx|1. Respond to all comments on your posts (5 min)
M|Dail|tx|2. Comment on 5-10 posts from target accounts (15 min)
M|Dail|tx|3. Share/repost w/ added in (5 min)
M|Dail|tx|4. Send 2-3 DMs to new connections (5 min)
M|Qual|it|Add new in, not just "Great post!"
